{"lang":"fr","stage":4,"title":"fuller short sentences","sentences":[{"t":"Tu connais cette chanson ?","en":"Do you know that song?","a":"n_f352c6fa8579.mp3"},{"t":"Bien sûr que tu peux.","en":"Of course you can.","a":"n_e95e21abe85d.mp3"},{"t":"C'est combien pour entrer ?","en":"How much does it cost to get in?","a":"n_d782a23336ba.mp3"},{"t":"Je devrais moins travailler.","en":"I should work less.","a":"n_5fcfc383df3f.mp3"},{"t":"Tu devrais savoir ça.","en":"You should know this.","a":"n_512c29e4177d.mp3"},{"t":"Il fait froid dehors ?","en":"Is it cold outside?","a":"n_8194e64fbb6e.mp3"},{"t":"Je fais mes devoirs.","en":"I'm doing the homework.","a":"n_f4e40044ee58.mp3"},{"t":"J'ai fait mes devoirs.","en":"I did my homework.","a":"n_842b41946d37.mp3"},{"t":"Fais pas ça.","en":"Don't do that.","a":"n_312727f4bacd.mp3"},{"t":"Dis-moi la vérité.","en":"Tell me the truth.","a":"n_d4ac0f320edd.mp3"},{"t":"Dis-moi qui c'était.","en":"Tell me who it was.","a":"n_a725a7d7864a.mp3"},{"t":"Demande-lui à elle.","en":"Ask her.","a":"n_f0b03c1713d2.mp3"},{"t":"Demande-lui combien il veut.","en":"Ask him how much he wants.","a":"n_93e981750121.mp3"},{"t":"Je t'en donne un.","en":"I'll give you one.","a":"n_1280c7c9988e.mp3"},{"t":"Je le cherche où ?","en":"Where do I look for it?","a":"n_b2316201f9e9.mp3"},{"t":"Je cherche mes clés.","en":"I'm looking for my keys.","a":"n_76228615f936.mp3"},{"t":"Je le trouve pas.","en":"I can't find it.","a":"n_4fd7bc398976.mp3"},{"t":"Je l'ai pas vu.","en":"I didn't see it.","a":"n_b41342508dc3.mp3"},{"t":"Vous avez une table ?","en":"Do you have a table?","a":"n_e7701f0a6655.mp3"},{"t":"Je veux acheter du pain.","en":"I want to buy bread.","a":"n_b737f6095977.mp3"},{"t":"Hier c'était dimanche.","en":"Yesterday was Sunday.","a":"n_38f2ba2516ac.mp3"},{"t":"Tu te sens bien ?","en":"Are you feeling okay?","a":"n_a68147943b1b.mp3"},{"t":"Comment tu te sens ?","en":"How do you feel?","a":"n_ead14c8e4630.mp3"},{"t":"J'ai besoin d'un cachet.","en":"I need a pill.","a":"n_2c9ea775b195.mp3"},{"t":"Je viens d'Espagne.","en":"I'm from Spain.","a":"n_92e4f68db5d9.mp3"},{"t":"Elle est occupée.","en":"She's busy.","a":"n_06101399ba27.mp3"},{"t":"Je dois y aller.","en":"I have to go.","a":"n_9a575db29429.mp3"},{"t":"T'es fâché contre moi ?","en":"Are you mad at me?","a":"n_159ab53c6a6e.mp3"},{"t":"Tu peux m'aider ?","en":"Can you help me?","a":"n_2d6ca78c0a9d.mp3"},{"t":"J'ai vingt ans.","en":"I'm twenty years old.","a":"n_f88befb470c6.mp3"},{"t":"J'ai besoin de ton aide.","en":"I need your help.","a":"n_51cf1e93b0f7.mp3"},{"t":"Je te dois combien ?","en":"How much do I owe you?","a":"n_3923ef40d5a1.mp3"},{"t":"Reviens pas tard.","en":"Don't come back late.","a":"n_158740f8d209.mp3"},{"t":"T'as fait quoi hier ?","en":"What did you do yesterday?","a":"n_64e495685841.mp3"},{"t":"On a fait un voyage.","en":"We took a trip.","a":"n_65dfbb957258.mp3"},{"t":"On le sait tous.","en":"We all know that.","a":"n_50860ab88a71.mp3"},{"t":"On sait pas.","en":"We don't know.","a":"n_3222fb47aeca.mp3"},{"t":"Tu vois la maison ?","en":"Do you see the house?","a":"n_bd09c7507bb9.mp3"},{"t":"Je te montre.","en":"I'll show you.","a":"n_4e5d6a87ad7c.mp3"},{"t":"Donne-moi la main.","en":"Give me your hand.","a":"n_72f180d955ae.mp3"},{"t":"Goûte un peu.","en":"Try a little.","a":"n_54bc8825112f.mp3"},{"t":"Demain c'est mardi.","en":"Tomorrow is Tuesday.","a":"n_d6d30c15aed9.mp3"},{"t":"Attends deux minutes.","en":"Wait two minutes.","a":"n_d6785f5f279f.mp3"},{"t":"Ça coûte vingt euros.","en":"They cost twenty euros.","a":"n_071c2cfb875d.mp3"},{"t":"J'ai deux frères.","en":"I have two brothers.","a":"n_59687ffb41eb.mp3"},{"t":"Tu dois faire attention.","en":"You must be careful.","a":"n_c89ecbbd70ce.mp3"},{"t":"Ils viennent demain.","en":"They're coming tomorrow.","a":"n_fd38346124be.mp3"},{"t":"On fait un plan.","en":"We're making a plan.","a":"n_c9fef8a737f4.mp3"},{"t":"Rends-moi un service.","en":"Do me a favor.","a":"n_ecfae64bd30a.mp3"},{"t":"Je veux te demander un truc.","en":"I want to ask you something.","a":"n_218bd12e5c0f.mp3"},{"t":"Je connais María.","en":"I know María.","a":"n_90976071a20b.mp3"},{"t":"Cherche-le à la maison.","en":"Look for it at home.","a":"n_f0c711f18e5d.mp3"},{"t":"Montre-moi la photo.","en":"Show me the photo.","a":"n_aca2f416db06.mp3"},{"t":"Je regarde la télé.","en":"I'm watching TV.","a":"n_927bedda04cd.mp3"},{"t":"Donne-moi une minute.","en":"Give me a minute.","a":"n_e0274f68bffa.mp3"},{"t":"Regarde qui est là.","en":"Look who's here.","a":"n_8f4ec96bc279.mp3"},{"t":"Je vais me doucher.","en":"I'm going to take a shower.","a":"n_177825b82e75.mp3"},{"t":"Tu te couches tard ?","en":"Do you go to bed late?","a":"n_b252cdc88150.mp3"},{"t":"Tu travailles ou tu étudies ?","en":"Do you work or study?","a":"n_120f21c2ccb8.mp3"},{"t":"On se lève ensemble.","en":"We get up together.","a":"n_95f59ee1242e.mp3"},{"t":"Tu me conseilles quoi ?","en":"What do you recommend?","a":"n_6fc1fed00ed3.mp3"},{"t":"Je déteste les lundis.","en":"I hate Mondays.","a":"n_a59643aca472.mp3"},{"t":"On est en janvier.","en":"It's January.","a":"n_4eb2b46df15d.mp3"},{"t":"Je paie en liquide.","en":"I'll pay in cash.","a":"n_f5fb24ad0853.mp3"},{"t":"Aujourd'hui c'est toi qui paies.","en":"Today you're paying.","a":"n_6f9951bbd0a6.mp3"},{"t":"Je suis malade aujourd'hui.","en":"I'm sick today.","a":"n_1f9b46a3862e.mp3"},{"t":"Bois beaucoup d'eau.","en":"Drink lots of water.","a":"n_807b58b02404.mp3"},{"t":"Donne-lui une chance.","en":"Give him a chance.","a":"n_9c28c1e2518b.mp3"},{"t":"Oui, c'est moi.","en":"Yes, that's me.","a":"n_72fe17a140a1.mp3"},{"t":"Oui, je le vois.","en":"Yes, I see it.","a":"n_faa020822dc7.mp3"},{"t":"Oui, je suis prêt.","en":"Yes, I'm ready.","a":"n_410af3357a42.mp3"},{"t":"Très bien, merci.","en":"Very well, thanks.","a":"n_e07b21da0a3f.mp3"},{"t":"Non, j'ai chaud.","en":"No, I'm hot.","a":"n_0975df7e88dc.mp3"},{"t":"Non, tourne là-bas.","en":"No, turn over there.","a":"n_92394555b1d6.mp3"},{"t":"Salut, je suis Carlos.","en":"Hi, I'm Carlos.","a":"n_8d89d32cd3d3.mp3"},{"t":"Bien sûr, tu peux demander.","en":"Sure, you can ask.","a":"n_ed547b9bc297.mp3"},{"t":"Regarde, j'ai compris.","en":"Look, now I get it.","a":"n_c76a01171dd7.mp3"},{"t":"Pardon, je suis perdu.","en":"Sorry, I'm lost.","a":"n_72d32dc52361.mp3"},{"t":"Salut, ça va ?","en":"Hi, how's it going?","a":"n_ed97a113cf1e.mp3"},{"t":"Ouais, je veux l'essayer.","en":"Yeah, I want to try it.","a":"n_aa433a227b57.mp3"},{"t":"Quand tu sors, préviens-moi.","en":"When you head out, let me know.","a":"n_fcd6b05e5521.mp3"},{"t":"Je sais pas ce que je veux.","en":"I don't know what I want.","a":"n_1a8a7db2ef0b.mp3"},{"t":"Je sais pas pourquoi.","en":"I don't know why.","a":"n_56cf8cd70e2c.mp3"},{"t":"Je suis pas chez moi.","en":"I'm not home.","a":"n_74c66c91e3d7.mp3"},{"t":"J'aime pas trop.","en":"I don't like it that much.","a":"n_f0198d40f3af.mp3"},{"t":"La maison est ici.","en":"The house is here.","a":"n_a2be59c422f9.mp3"},{"t":"Elle est d'ici.","en":"She's from here.","a":"n_7a75a320d5c6.mp3"},{"t":"J'aime le café.","en":"I like coffee.","a":"n_2c02aaa96598.mp3"},{"t":"Tu aimes le café ?","en":"Do you like coffee?","a":"n_f0b0f362f9f7.mp3"},{"t":"Je sais rien.","en":"I don't know anything.","a":"n_7c0d6a35644c.mp3"},{"t":"Je peux rien manger.","en":"I can't eat anything.","a":"n_e41815630b71.mp3"},{"t":"Je vais manger un truc.","en":"I'm going to eat something.","a":"n_d336b016dc0c.mp3"},{"t":"Je veux un truc à manger.","en":"I want something to eat.","a":"n_d1cf2c690a91.mp3"},{"t":"Je vais manger maintenant.","en":"I'm going to eat now.","a":"n_a2042b835920.mp3"}]}